{"title":"[JL][基础]CJX爱几何","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-5834","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>等腰直角三角形：三角形中有一个角是直角，且两条直角边相等。</p><p>这里我们输出直角边长为n的等腰直角三角形的格式如下所示：</p><p>比如n=1，则输出：</p><p>*</p><p>n=2，输出：</p><p>*</p><p>**</p><p>n=3，输出：</p><p>*</p><p>**</p><p>***</p><p>CJX很喜欢这个题目，他不想自己画就可以每天欣赏这种图形</p><p>你能用程序帮助他来实现么？</p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">输入一个数</span><span style=\"font-family: '';\">n</span><span style=\"\">，表示三角形的边长。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 22.8571434020996px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\">输出对应的等腰直角三角形。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>   </p><pre style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;\">4</pre><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>   </p><pre style=\"font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;\">*\n**\n***\n****</pre><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>[JL]超基础题目</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}